'''草氨酸'''是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，[[化学式|化学式]]为H<sub>2</sub>NC(=O)CO<sub>2</sub>H。它是白色固体，可溶于水，是[[草酸|草酸]]的单[[酰胺|酰胺]]衍生物。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/compound/oxamic_acid#section=Depositor-Supplied-Synonyms |title=OXAMIC ACID |publisher=Pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov |date= |accessdate=2016-12-14 |archive-date=2016-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161201014207/https://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/compound/oxamic_acid#section=Depositor-Supplied-Synonyms |dead-url=no }}</ref>草氨酸可以抑制{{link-en|LDHA|Lactate dehydrogenase A}}。<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0085576 |pmid=24465604 |pmc=3897486 |title=Synergistic Anti-Cancer Effect of Phenformin and Oxamate |journal=PLoS ONE |volume=9 |issue=1 |pages=e85576 |year=2014 |last1=Miskimins |first1=W. Keith |last2=Ahn |first2=Hyun Joo |last3=Kim |first3=Ji Yeon |last4=Ryu |first4=Sun |last5=Jung |first5=Yuh-Seog |last6=Choi |first6=Joon Young }}</ref>
==化学性质==
草氨酸可以和金属[[碳酸盐|碳酸盐]]反应，形成[[草氨酸盐|草氨酸盐]]。<ref>Caires, F.J., Lima, L.S., Carvalho, C.T. ''et al.'' Thermal and spectroscopic data to investigate the oxamic acid, sodium oxamate and its compounds with some bivalent transition metal ions. ''J Therm Anal Calorim'' (2012) 107: 335. doi:10.1007/s10973-011-1835-8</ref>

